{"tid":950611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖]有得食唔食?大陸妹","createTime":"2018-12-21T16:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T03:39:02.000Z","uid":175761,"like":99,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0730ff2a46b7a9a086732f65fd691be863156026","tid":950611,"uid":175761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:20:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n識左個大陸妹係香港做野既,食過幾次飯<br />\n言談間佢chok我有冇女，24號有冇街去<br />\n想我帶佢去玩(24號)<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女  樣:中等  身材: B/C  行路個陣佢成日借D意請我食波餅<br />\n唔知係咪大陸妹唔care<br />\n同佢發展最多散拖，冇乜Feel<br />\n<br />\n究竟去唔去馬好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說2年前有相似情況，不過係NDS<br />\n當時因為其他野冇去馬，有後悔<br />\n<br />\n巴打覺得我去唔去馬好?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌完先至講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放生人啦仆街 / 大陸妹有手尾跟  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d34e09f0b6f06e3c1a7eeae2d086b2e262c444d","tid":950611,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d682b8feebb217c8f73b54b61c969947f0f101a6","tid":950611,"uid":175761,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4d34e09f0b6f06e3c1a7eeae2d086b2e262c444d","tid":950611,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T16:32:38.000Z","msg":"你真係24小時MON住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403969a7c1f5f921bc8ccc391ac874fb6921d18c","tid":950611,"uid":39245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d682b8feebb217c8f73b54b61c969947f0f101a6","tid":950611,"uid":175761,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4d34e09f0b6f06e3c1a7eeae2d086b2e262c444d","tid":950611,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1